summary: A scavenger never wastes a weapon he/she finds
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][size=6][b]Weapons Of Nature

[/b][/size][size=4]The First Weapon to make its way into the mod is the Icicle
More Weapons on the way

[/size][size=3]Its a very high poly model with 4K textures
The Icicle is translucent (Enb mileage will vary)[/size]

[size=4]Installation[/size]
[size=3]The mod is Nexus Mod Manager ready just download and install 
Use the Console ` to obtain the Weapon in game
type "help Icicle 0" without quotes [/size][/center]
